meta_description: Brittany McGlone, 19, was sexually assaulted and murdered while she slept at her boyfriend's house in Winnsboro, Texas on May 4, 2007. She had just finished a night shift at the Lowe’s Distribution Center in Mount Vernon, and went to her boyfriend’s house to sleep. Nothing was stolen from the house and there were no signs of forced entry. There are suspects in the case, but no one has been publicly named. The Wood County Sheriff's Office is investigating.
